@startuml
!include _style.iuml
title 【Loop2・新規】コミュニケーション図 UC5：予約をキャンセルする

actor 利用者 as guest
rectangle ":DeleteReservationForm" <<boundary>> as form #FFE6CC
rectangle ":DeleteReservationControl" <<control>> as control #FFE6CC
rectangle ":ReservationManager" <<control>> as resm
rectangle ":RoomManager" <<control>> as rm
rectangle ":Reservation" <<entity>> as res
rectangle ":AvailableQty" <<entity>> as aq

guest --> form : 1: deleteReservation()
form --> control : 2: deleteReservation(予約番号)
control --> resm : 3: cancelReservation(予約番号)
resm --> res : 3.1: 予約を削除する（未利用のみ）
control --> rm : 4: updateRoomAvailableQty(宿泊日, +1)
rm --> aq : 4.1: 空室数を1増やす（在庫を戻す）
@enduml
